---
title: Speedy Honey-Garlic Tofu Stir-Fry with Green Onion Rice
description: Tofu is the secret to stir-fry that's both speedy and scrumptious! In this fast fry, crumbled tofu is smothered in a sweet and savoury honey-garlic sauce and paired with sweet bell peppers and tender-crisp zucchini.
